				<td colspan="2"><span>Be very careful if you attempt what CeleadorKB is suggesting.  Siren's is somewhat of a death trap with almost all battle underwater, and many wandering adds as well as adds around every corner.  If you know the zone inside-and-out and are very comfortable using invis underwater to pass some 20 mobs to solo these princesses, give it a whirl.  It's exceptionally dangerous in my eyes.
<br />

<br />
The charm idea is a little better, but still very risky.  The thing he is suggesting you charm hits very hard, heaven forbid charm breaks while you're down there.
